{"tid":484435,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"(金牌大律師) 清洪: 強姦案難入罪","createTime":"2017-11-30T05:38:51.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-30T12:23:04.000Z","uid":134071,"like":14,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"7caf1acefa2f5ad0215ee4f25b974d19d48c3056","tid":484435,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-30T05:38:52.000Z","msg":"清洪在《金牙大狀教你講中講英》一書的Page 130中, 講明強姦案難入罪.  強姦案不只在印度入罪率低,  在瑞典、美國及英國的強姦案入罪率也很低.<br />\n<a href=\"http://books.google.com.hk/books?id=tvOQAwAAQBAJ&amp;dq\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbooks.google.com.hk%2Fbooks%3Fid%3DtvOQAwAAQBAJ%26dq&d=OmBJcyTWCAlw5rhpG6lzZ7ZGMQxn7aheim1dKZ3ASAU%3D&h=f2d91eee\" target=\"_blank\">http://books.google.com.hk/books?id=tvOQAwAAQBAJ&amp;dq</a><br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\">於印度,由1971年至2012 年期間,報稱被強姦及最終提出檢控的比例從百分之四十六下跌至百分之二十六。然而,瑞典、美國及英國的強姦案入罪率則更低,這些國家的警察一般都會力勸受辱的女士放棄投訴。</span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n另一方面, 強姦案係香港的入罪率也很低.<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.rainlily.org.hk/down_file.php?type=reports&amp;id=53\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.rainlily.org.hk%2Fdown_file.php%3Ftype%3Dreports%26id%3D53&d=OmBJcyTWCAlw5rhpG6lzZ7ZGMQxn7aheim1dKZ3ASAU%3D&h=9a9e1ab4\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.rainlily.org.hk/down_file.php?type=reports&amp;id=53</a><br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\">根據警方統計顯示，於 2010 年至 2013 年 6 月期間，警方接獲強姦及非禮的案件數目分別為 383 及 5117 宗，而於同期被裁定干犯強姦及非禮罪行的人數分別為 75 及 1476 人。上述兩類罪行入罪率分別約為 19.6%及 28.8%，即是強姦案入罪率比非禮案低於五成。強姦案的入罪率竟如此之低，這實在使人沮喪。</span><br />\n<br />\n無辦法, 在「疑點利益歸於被告」的情況下,  強姦案難入罪是可以理解."},{"pid":"f7fa288fac7947d580c02357daf78e647adcbf04","tid":484435,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-30T05:39:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"03ca2767a92838d704985125e12807db70269673","tid":484435,"uid":531,"like":16,"dislike":2,"score":14,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-30T05:41:04.000Z","msg":"開哂名告唔入被告都夠慘"},{"pid":"07abd959182662d3d9a9